<br>
last night i fought a lower level doc (48, i was 53) and i totaly kicked his ass, to the point where he ran out of tir arena and zoned into that nicely placed building right next to the arena...now either he sucked, or docs are less effective in pvp now, because back october a doc would have eaten a MA alive just because you couldnt kill a doc until they ran out of nano.. but then i fought a lower level enforcer (45) and i died, fought a higher level agent that was doing false prof meta to use meta pets, got his heal pet dead and him to 3/4 life but then died cause i ran out of nano to heal myself hehe, fought a same level nano-tech, he rooted me a couple times but the second root he didnt get out of range in time, and i knocked him with a quick BwT followed by dimach and he was taking a dirt nap.... so im guessing casters would be MA's main targets, but without range (yet) attacks we are kinda root bait....<br>
<br>
