<br>
at lvl 53 like you are..u can probably own just about anyone..if you are twinked out as much as you can be. the best implants,armor you can put on. get the best heal you can get (remember team heals heal almost as much and recharge way faster). get the highest bwt you can. and keep dimach maxed. only use dimach as a finishing move also. never do it at the front of a fight..especially when fighting healers. <br>
<br>
agents...these will probably give u the most trouble and never fight a titled trader. agents and traders who pvp are twinked out as can be. a twinked enforcer will probably also own u..but maybe not. kinda depends who crits the most.<br>
<br>
soldiers...just keep healing till their shield wears off. start fight in max defense to try and decrease dmg of their alpha strike.<br>
<br>
anyone else who roots just keep running at them when root breaks and pound the crap out of them. if u go to mmd or 2ho try to get a crit/ac/HP buff. outside buffs at the arena are frowned upon cuz you are fighting other clanners. <br>
